summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the payment of, the cost and expense of the condemnation of 29th Avenue South, from Bennett Street to Americus Street; 28th Avenue South from Americus Street to Alaska Street, as established by Ordinance No. 39643; 30th Avenue South, from Bennett Street to Edmunds Street; Edmunds Street, from 30th Avenue South to 32nd Avenue South, as provided in Ordinance No. 45500 of the City of Seattle, and repealing Ordinance No. 48361.
